    "In this section we give a broad overview of contributions using VAE, GAN and, DDPM.Variational Autoencoders (VAE).",
    "Over the last few years, modified and extended versions of the Variational Autoencoder have been developed to solve problems in a variety of scientific fields [41,42,43,44,45].",
